show.description: A powerful fusion of love, betrayal, and ambition begins as powerful families clash. In this game of legacy, old secrets emerge… secrets that not only shake empires but also break hearts. Amidst blood ties and broken promises — will love survive, or will it become the next casualty? Witness a high-stakes drama where emotions run deep, loyalties are tested, and every truth comes at a price.
